    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1 provisions for MRL 2. CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission decision that the worst-case hemolysis operating condition has been correctly identified, with RH = 0.87 satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Assessment accepted with no outstanding action items.",
